name: Podiatry Center of New Jersey, LLC

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Podiatry Center of New Jersey, LLC is a Clinic/Center, Podiatric provider based in Wayne, NJ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $57.1M in Medicaid payments across 545K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $57.1M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
